To ensure inclusivity, we launched AI WikiCat coin ($AIWKC) available to everyone on PancakeSwap V2.

Liquidity

To ensure the security and stability of our Liquidity Pool, 100% LP is locked. We have also renounced contract ownership and have ensured that no harmful functions are present in our code.

Community Driven

Our community members who hold $AIWKC will be eligible to connect to our free education portal which focuses on AI innovations. Holders will also be eligible to claim NFT pets.

Future Driven

The first potential use of AI to scale and invites solutions, innovation, and ML (Machine Learning) to the Meme coin space. Ai WikiCat is the Future.

Low slippage

AI WikiCat as a meme coin furthers the adoption of low slippage of easy transactions being a community-driven project

Development Wallet

4% of the coin is locked into a multi-signature marketing wallet this allows the team to update the website and run marketing promotions.

How To Buy

Create Metamask Wallet

Create a MetaMask Wallet using either a desktop computer or an iOS/Android. This will allow you to buy, sell, send, and receive $AIWKC

Send BNB To Your Wallet

You can buy BNB directly on MetaMask or transfer it to your MetaMask Wallet from exchanges like Binance, Kucoin, etc.

Swap BNB For AIWKC

When you have BNB available, Press ‘Select a token’ and enter the token address  0x6b4570a4452cec85aeb5de8b6883b17c4f638460 Click the swap button & confirm the transaction
